Caption.String: In Value mode, the growth rate applies to the previous year's annual kWh load starting in Year 2. In Schedule mode, each year's rate applies to the Year 1 kWh value. See Help for details.

Description.String: Type a fraction for each hour of the day.
Type a one (on) or zero (off) for each hour of the day.
Type a load growth rate (%) for each year. Each year's growth rate applies to the total annual load in Year 1.
